Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:19.97,Song,,0,0,0,,If only there were no tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:23.70,Song,,0,0,0,,School would've been a fun place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:30.04,Song,,0,0,0,,I never cared much for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:38.56,Song,,0,0,0,,I just stared out the window all through class,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:44.60,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}Always dreaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:52.54,Song,,0,0,0,,But if I'd at least taken English seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.85,Song,,0,0,0,,By now I'd be some cool international girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:07.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study a little than not at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:12.96,Song,,0,0,0,,There must be at least one thing you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:22.57,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study while you still have the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:28.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Realizing too late won't help you then.
