Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:40.05,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:48.52,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:56.69,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:04.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:11.81,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:22.22,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:31.83,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:33.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\q2\an9\fs20\bord0.3\blur1\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro B\pos(431.23,256)\c&HFDFDFD&}Translation \NEditing \N 
