Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.65,0:01:39.03,Top,,0,0,0,,King Arthur was a legendary Celtic hero,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.65,Top,,0,0,0,,and some say he really lived between the fifth and sixth centuries.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.14,0:01:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,His kingdom was called Logres, \Nand most of it was what we now call England, {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logres}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.21,0:01:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but the tales also spread to Scotland, Wales, Cornwall, Ireland, and even Brittany in France.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.49,0:02:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The main stories tell of Arthur’s stormy life
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as the conqueror of England and Gaul,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course, of the wizard Merlin...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.68,0:02:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you all know the Knights \Nof the Round Table, don’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They were the brave knights \Nwho served King Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.81,0:02:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the greatest of them all was Lancelot.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.92,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right, Lancelot’s gallant exploits \Nand his secret romance with Queen Guinevere.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.85,0:02:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all so romantic, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could meet them! {?????? aitai wa?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.40,0:02:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, a castle has been discovered \Nup in the hills just beyond Rensing, {can't find any real such place, so safe to assume it's just a contrived generic english toponym}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.79,0:02:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and they say it may well \Nhave some link to King Arthur.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really true, Miss Lewis?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.43,0:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, Saturday afternoon, \Nwe’ll go there to visit the ruins.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to come?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.92,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely must come!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now don’t forget, \Nyou’re not coming just for a picnic. {hiking}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But you did say we could \Nbring along some sweets, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.95,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did grant permission,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But you never thought \Nit would be on such a scale!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we did restrain ourselves, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right. {mimicking lewis}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.99,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this castle ruin we’re going to see now may be closely connected to Lancelot.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I simply adore Lancelot!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of connection is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve heard of Sir Meliagrance, haven’t you? {"meriaguraisu" in japanese, one of alternative readings of https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maleagant}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.71,0:04:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one day when Queen Guinevere \Nwas out in the woods picking flowers,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.41,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Meliagrance, one of the Round Table knights, \Nsuddenly attacked her and carried her off to his castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he do such a horrid thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.57,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in secret Meliagrance \Nwas in love with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.63,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Fancy that, Queen Guinevere \Nwas as popular as me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll go a long way, \Nsaying things like that. {lit: you'll live a long life - idiomatic slang for when someone blurts out something cheeky, silly, or overconfident — as if “with that kind of cheek, you’ll go on forever.”}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.57,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one who rode straight to her rescue \Nwas none other than Sir Lancelot.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.11,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly so. Lancelot charged in all alone, \Ncutting down wave after wave of foes,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.45,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,until at last Meliagrance grew frightened \Nand begged Queen Guinevere to spare his life.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t Lancelot marvellous!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d love to meet him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.60,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Some even say it wasn’t Meliagrance’s castle at all, \Nbut the very one we’re going to visit
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.89,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,where Guinevere was taken prisoner. \NAnd I’m inclined to believe it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How thrilling!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.06,0:05:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, Miss Lewis, \Nyou don’t mean that’s all there is?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that’s all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.65,0:05:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we’d find a proper castle standing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,True! I’m dreadfully disappointed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.95,0:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, from these few remains \Nwe can tell it was a castle of Arthur’s time,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.42,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and it does fit the idea that Queen Guinevere might once have been held prisoner here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve learnt quite a lot already.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.12,0:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what I’d like you to do \Nis stand here a while and see what you feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.69,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up, for example, \Nat this moss-covered tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.70,0:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of Lancelot, Queen Guinevere, and Sir Meliagrance.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.11,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you feel something stirring?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.98,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps the view itself—\Nthe sky, the hills, the lake.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn’t it give you a sense of something?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.20,0:06:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not come at once, but keep it in mind \Nas you wander about the place in your own way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just walk about, Miss?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.54,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You never know, you might stumble upon something linked to the castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.65,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Isabel, did you feel anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But just once, I wish I could meet him.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancelot, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.39,0:07:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking the very same thing just now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.63,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Pat, I have come to rescue you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.53,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancelot! Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel, over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels as if we’ve strayed \Ninto some strange place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! A sound.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.05,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.89,0:08:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A horse!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.06,0:08:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s follow it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are those people?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How odd!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.21,0:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Odd? They look exactly like folk \Nfrom King Arthur’s time!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.45,0:09:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a film shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who’s starring, I wonder?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait... {/it's strange}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no director, \Nno cameras, no crew anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.57,0:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps a Shakespearean troupe rehearsing?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.54,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of doors? \NI’ve never heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.53,0:09:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sir Meliagrance?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.25,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the depths of the forest, \Nthere blooms a field of beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My! Pray guide me there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.99,0:09:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He called her Queen Guinevere, \Nand himself Meliagrance!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.23,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve slipped back \Ninto King Arthur’s time!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Surely not...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.83,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is, let’s follow and see!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.39,0:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide there! {???? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must come with me, Queen Guinevere.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. Be my wife!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.78,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Meliagrance! \NThat is no way to speak to the Queen!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They are slaughtering them for real! {lit: really killed - think she means "this is not staged"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Flee at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you’ll be shut up inside the castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.95,0:11:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your tongue!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, Meliagrance.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down your sword.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.54,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will come with me, will you not?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.51,0:11:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Queen. We’re from St. Clare's School,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.11,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and Isabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re twins.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, twins?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way. {/I'll come with you}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.66,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.94,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t Lancelot of the Round Table\N supposed to come to the rescue?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.45,0:12:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must warn him at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Lancelot, knight of King Arthur’s Round Table!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is me...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m Pat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.10,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I’m Isabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Guinevere...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,has been carried off by Meliagrance!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? Where to?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll show you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.93,0:13:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come then!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel, isn’t this the very place \NMiss Lewis brought us to?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.89,0:14:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I’m sure of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So a castle...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,once stood here after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on it will be dangerous, \Nso you must get down.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we must part here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we can’t bear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to stay with you always!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I would take you with me,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.53,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but a battle is about to begin.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get down, won’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Lancelot.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be obvious!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.92,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Meliagrance!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Meliagrance!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.73,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What business have you with me, Lancelot?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.97,0:15:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you carry off the Queen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.00,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand her over quietly, \Nor I shall strike you down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you hope to do alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! {?? sore?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What folly!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He really rode in all alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How gallant! {/cool}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho there, Guinevere! \NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.10,0:16:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, where can she be? {?? i assume she's imitating lancelot's oi}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s try over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, Guinevere! Come forth!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, Guinevere!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s happening here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.39,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi! You shan’t escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho, this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Miss Lewis!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,Janet, Kathleen, Hilary, Alison!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.64,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,And Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What’s going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.05,0:17:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are, over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.25,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.23,0:17:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancelot! Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.77,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! \NHe couldn’t have come this far alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.54,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that! {?? lit: How about this one?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.24,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancelot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thou wretch...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the queen to safety!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t let them get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Perish, Lancelot! {???? only hear lancelot}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that? {meaning "why is there a pressable stone in the floor"}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An exit!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all three of you unhurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancelot!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.28,0:19:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lancelot!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, Isabel—thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall never forget you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.21,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor shall we ever forget you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.11,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{bunch of pat and isabel}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They opened their eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.56,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.06,0:19:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We are!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet we are! {/isn't that obvious}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.83,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re coming down now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.38,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have Lancelot \Nand Queen Guinevere gone?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, twins?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, \Nwhat are we talking about? {or "isn't it obvious what are we talking about"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There really was a castle here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.44,0:20:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! And we truly spoke \Nwith Lancelot and Queen Guinevere.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.12,0:20:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t we?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve banged your heads and gone daft, \Nhaven’t you, twins?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing of the sort, \Nwe really did see them!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Queen thanked us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lancelot said he’d never forget us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be marvellous if it were true...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can’t believe it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Lewis!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they slipped back in time?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m certain of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.67,0:20:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don’t know \Nif such a thing is truly possible,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.98,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but at any rate, you two seem to have had \Na mysterious experience. {/strange}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.41,0:20:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious indeed—to think you both \Nhad the very same dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.15,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s twin magic for you. {lit: that's the strange/mysterious part of being twins}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.19,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it’s something you could never do \Nwithout using all your imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.93,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to think of people of long ago \Nas merely figures from the past,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but imagine them as if they were alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.77,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the smallest detail may become a clue, \Nand suddenly it all takes shape.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.34,0:21:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, history is not simply learning dates by rote.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.55,0:21:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The harder you try to understand it,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the more history itself seems to speak to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.49,0:21:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Guinevere was truly gracious \Nand kind at heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Radiantly beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.21,0:21:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sir Lancelot of the Round Table
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.51,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was noble, brave, strong, \Nand the most splendid of all!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I’m envious!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.79,0:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I wish I’d tumbled over that cliff too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.02,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you'd only have fainted then, that’s all.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.69,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Janet!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.33,0:23:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, Pat, Alison’s gone on a diet.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.38,0:23:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She says unless she’s pretty, \Nboys won’t even glance at her.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.84,0:23:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense! \NWho needs a diet? I can't believe my ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.72,0:23:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But the others have started too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.59,0:23:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely not you as well, Isabel?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.10,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.72,0:23:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is dreadful!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.42,0:23:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever shall we do \Nabout the lacrosse match?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.94,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twins at St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Dieting Craze!" {みんなでダイエット!}{lit: everyone diets}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t miss it!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.36,0:24:04.81,Note,,0,0,0,,Episode 24 \NA Dieting Craze! {みんなでダイエット!}
